The paper discusses the security and privacy-enhancing mechanisms in vehicular communication systems, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and network security (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the impact of these mechanisms on transportation safety, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also mentions the need for appropriate system design, which could involve artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and software engineering (cs.SE).
